		<div>Slightly off-topic - as I read this list, I notice that the wizard issues are broader in depth to what is desired compared to what I read about the bard issues.  Whereas questions about the lure and pillar lines are asked - numerous wizards using the same spells instead of having spells continuously throughout their advancing levels, as but one example - the bards are asking to make the weapon &quot;Songblade of the Eternal&quot; inventory clickable.  The good of the many wizards compared to the rarity of the bard obtaining this weapon from Innoruuk in the Plane of Time.<br />
